	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think it's a good idea to use a function pointer that handles decoding on a mapper basis instead of predefined banks. That way there isn't overhead on simple mappers and the actual mapper functionality can be carried out at the same time.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


